NAME
    Alien::Gfsm - install the libgfsm C library on your system

SYNOPSIS
       use 5.010;
       use strict;
       use Alien::Gfsm;
   
       my $alien = Alien::Gfsm->new;
       say $alien->libs;
       say $alien->cflags;

DESCRIPTION
    Ensures that the libgfsm C library is installed on your system.

AUTHOR
    Bryan Jurish <moocow@cpan.org>.

